        <a href="#diagnostic" class="btn btn-outline">See how a diagnosis works ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section id="diagnostic" class="diagnostic-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">How a service call goes</span>
        <h2>Run the same scan John runs on a broken system.</h2>
        <p>Every irrigation problem leaves a clue — low pressure, a wet spot, a zone that won't shut off. Tap the button to step through five real Riverview calls, from first symptom to fix.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="diag-panel device-panel reveal">
        <span class="screw tl"></span><span class="screw tr"></span><span class="screw bl"></span><span class="screw br"></span>
        <div class="diag-top">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--brass-deep);">Zone schematic</span>
          <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--ink-soft);">CONTROLLER → MAINLINE → VALVE → HEAD → BODY</span>
