            <label>Outcome</label>
            <p class="diag-time"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="zones" class="zones-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Select a zone</span>
        <h2>Six things John gets called for</h2>
        <p>Numbered the way your controller already numbers its zones — pick the one that matches what's going on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="zones-grid">

        <div class="zone-card reveal">
          <div class="zone-top">
            <span class="zone-num">01</span>
            <svg class="zone-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 2v3M12 19v3M4.2 4.2l2.1 2.1M17.7 17.7l2.1 2.1M2 12h3M19 12h3M4.2 19.8l2.1-2.1M17.7 6.3l2.1-2.1"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Leak Detection &amp; Diagnosis</h3>
          <p>Find what's actually wrong before anything gets replaced — including breaks that never surface as a puddle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="zone-card reveal">
          <div class="zone-top">
            <span class="zone-num">02</span>
            <svg class="zone-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2l7 4v6c0 5-3.5 8-7 10-3.5-2-7-5-7-10V6z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Valve &amp; Sprinkler Head Repair</h3>
          <p>Stuck valves, cracked bodies, and heads that stopped spraying — fixed on the spot, same visit.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="zone-card reveal">
          <div class="zone-top">
            <span class="zone-num">03</span>
            <svg class="zone-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="4" y="5" width="16" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M9 9h6M9 12h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Controller Install &amp; Programming</h3>
          <p>A new timer, corrected wiring, or a watering schedule that finally matches your yard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="zone-card reveal">
          <div class="zone-top">
            <span class="zone-num">04</span>
            <svg class="zone-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 12a8 8 0 0 1 14-5"/><path d="M20 12a8 8 0 0 1-14 5"/><path d="M18 3v4h-4M6 21v-4h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Seasonal Tune-Ups</h3>
          <p>Purge the lines, rebalance every head, and adjust coverage before the season turns.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="zone-card reveal">
          <div class="zone-top">
            <span class="zone-num">05</span>
            <svg class="zone-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 12h4l3-8 4 16 3-8h4"/></svg>
